{"tid":2165132,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"分享下Display Card降電壓效果","createTime":"2020-08-19T15:18:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T21:11:25.000Z","uid":16873,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"26951e24eb9c21c53f412806a631e5d72278e391","tid":2165132,"uid":16873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T15:18:56.000Z","msg":"呢排成日見人問張GPU好熱可以點搞，咁降電壓就係一招唔使俾任何錢，收益又好高嘅方法<br />\n首先介紹下我嘅配置<br />\nNcase m1<br />\nStrix 2080 super A8G<br />\n機底冇加任何風扇，純靠張卡本身3把風扇入風<br />\n<br />\n咁先睇下stock情況下跑3dmark timespy stress test嘅結果<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yDi01Yz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyDi01Yz.png&h=e8ef8508&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跑7分鐘左右已經去到77度，呢個時候gpu clock係行緊1890mhz，電壓喺1v - 1.02v左右<br />\n<br />\n再睇下手動降壓到0.9v嘅結果<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OcxJfjt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOcxJfjt.png&h=a7381f57&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n跑15分鐘都只係71度，而gpu clock同樣係1890mhz，免費降咗6度<br />\n我呢張2080s體質好普通，再降電壓就跑唔到stress test，果然a8g係廢過o8g<br />\n<br />\n最後結論係非常值得一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲買平卡嘅人就算機箱點加風扇都幫助唔大，因為壓住gpu嘅cooler太廢，只有源頭減少發熱先會有效果<br />\n至於詳細要點操作就交俾澳洲佬<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zUkPAVcb9Xc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzUkPAVcb9Xc&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufRphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=96ee1832\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zUkPAVcb9Xc</a>"},{"pid":"725e46b866da36bf01e2b140241c566df1b2aeba","tid":2165132,"uid":137096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T15:22:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03af6a7306036907aa87490f52823dc5ba2b3bc2","tid":2165132,"uid":16873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T15:31:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eab106992adde034d3beb59d4002ca75af6e3249","tid":2165132,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T15:33:11.000Z","msg":"rog 唔係輕鬆低過70度咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92653de81b1c8e40dee10a3b7ef7efb26a47805e","tid":2165132,"uid":16873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eab106992adde034d3beb59d4002ca75af6e3249","tid":2165132,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T15:33:11.000Z","msg":"rog 唔係輕鬆低過70度咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T15:35:34.000Z","msg":"itx箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我睇reddit strix卡仲可以喺底加2把薄扇，不過我懶得搞"},{"pid":"5213c5cd8a237541fd9c8c1d759eed05ef64640d","tid":2165132,"uid":334722,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"eab106992adde034d3beb59d4002ca75af6e3249","tid":2165132,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T15:33:11.000Z","msg":"rog 唔係輕鬆低過70度咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T16:00:37.000Z","msg":"ROG上到2080Ti都係六十零度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n痴撚線...真係貴得有道理"},{"pid":"202d7ba4a84e4dbe42508ec0144d997aa140692f","tid":2165132,"uid":191510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T17:47:39.000Z","msg":"係高階卡預設食好多電<br />\n<br />\n但實際跟本降一兩成Power你超返上去都可以穩定跑同一個頻率<br />\n<br />\n因為佢睇GPU BOOST 4.0做人(愈低溫愈好超)<br />\n<br />\n變相你散熱屎不如比少D電,超返上去效果會仲好"},{"pid":"29c96eafb1b647f8b5a4f409b2f06abd6df639f2","tid":2165132,"uid":341040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T18:56:36.000Z","msg":"屌 正呀<br />\n最近用緊450銅牛推2070 + i7 4790<br />\n<br />\nundervolt左唔洗買新psu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d2c092fc365bc7915173a824b666f228b0fbb69","tid":2165132,"uid":239558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T19:01:40.000Z","msg":"5700xt 公版用家表示：長期90度未驚過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489ad7f630604a0bca1d8ab75890febd3e4a015d","tid":2165132,"uid":9103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d2c092fc365bc7915173a824b666f228b0fbb69","tid":2165132,"uid":239558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T19:01:40.000Z","msg":"5700xt 公版用家表示：長期90度未驚過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T21:11:25.000Z","msg":"非公版用家唔開冷氣一打機就8x度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />feel到陣熱浪"}]}